{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CyberGuard Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #1a237e; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-blue: #536dfe; /* Lighter, complementary blue */\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0; /* Light gray for text */\n            --background-color: #0d1117; /* Dark background */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: rgba(26, 35, 126, 0.3); /* Slightly transparent brand blue */\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(83, 110, 254, 0.5); /* Subtle border */\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic Effects */\n        .header-art::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n                -45deg,\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05),\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 5px,\n                transparent 5px,\n                transparent 10px\n            );\n            z-index: 0;\n            opacity: 0.6;\n        }\n\n        .section-art::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(83, 110, 254, 0.1) 0%, rgba(83, 110, 254, 0) 50%);\n            z-index: -1;\n            opacity: 0.4;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Keyframes for subtle animation */\n        @keyframes pulsate {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 1; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n        }\n\n        .service-item:nth-child(odd) {\n            animation: pulsate 5s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .service-item:nth-child(even) {\n            animation: pulsate 5s infinite ease-in-out reverse;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"header-art\">\n        <h1>CyberGuard Solutions</h1>\n        <p>Fortifying Your Digital Frontier</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At CyberGuard Solutions, we are dedicated to providing cutting-edge cybersecurity services to protect your business from evolving digital threats. Our team of experts leverages advanced technologies and strategic insights to ensure the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of your critical data.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\" class=\"section-art\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Threat Detection & Response</h3>\n                    <p>Proactive monitoring and rapid response to security incidents, minimizing damage and downtime.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Vulnerability Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>Identifying and prioritizing weaknesses in your systems before they can be exploited.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Penetration Testing</h3>\n                    <p>Simulating real-world attacks to uncover exploitable vulnerabilities.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n                    <p>Expert advice and strategic planning to build robust security frameworks.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Data Encryption</h3>\n                    <p>Implementing strong encryption protocols to safeguard sensitive information.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Compliance & Governance</h3>\n                    <p>Ensuring adherence to industry regulations and best practices.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Ready to secure your business? Reach out to our experts today.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@cybeguardsolutions.com\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-blue); text-decoration: none;\">info@cybeguardsolutions.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: +1 (800) 555-CYBG</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 CyberGuard Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}